data.description: Enjoy this beautiful 5 BR, 3Bth 4 level home. Double walkout, 3 fireplaces 3 season solarium/sun porch with heated floor. Huge family room with a walkout. Lower level large amusement room with walkout. Dining room leads to sun room with heated floor. New carpet and paint throughout the house. Granite countertops in the kitchen and in all bathrooms. New light fixtures. Open floor plan with great sunlight. Next to Woodhill Park & close to freeways.
